{"tid":2425430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（長）香港人真係賤種，正垃圾，大家都係中國人！","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:41:54.000Z","uid":2719,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0511cd887c84869c81ad7e8dcf7a3456545c1620","tid":2425430,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"只要自己鍾意睇就合理化所有野，<br />\n忘記一切國家情仇（香港國）<br />\n<br />\n早排試當真cctvb、依家三叔護旗手，只要自己鍾意睇，就會揾無數籍口合理化之前自己屌嘅事，wfc良知。<br />\n<br />\n更甚嘅係當堅持良知嘅人作岀提醒，反而會被屌為反而反同無人性，圍攻立場鮮明嘅人係非黑即白嘅垃圾（明明國家情仇一直都應該係非黑即白無中立）。<br />\n<br />\n好心啦講地位，成龍係影視界同校長係歌壇遠超三叔十萬九千里啦，將來係咪又話佢地為香港軟實力貢獻多要rip？<br />\n<br />\n又想屈人00後無睇過唔明？咁到時有人rip成龍校長係咪又可以屌你90後無睇過唔明啊？<br />\n<br />\n根本(深入經歷同體驗）2019年嘅人，呢方面嘅事一定馬上劃清界線，仇恨值高到無可能幫諗籍口。<br />\n<br />\n人地兩公婆都可以因為政見而離婚，你地同三叔嘅感情仲重過兩公婆？<br />\n<br />\n晒氣啦！正垃圾一鍾意就變左膠，仲敢叫自己係香港人，坐緊/逃走/去了的真香港人如果知道你地為護旗手護航，真係心都淡晒，當年為你呢班人而拚命，真不值！"},{"pid":"b08e70a613d2d6194a6af42154fd85996556c636","tid":2425430,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"達哥 rip<br />\n<br />\n利申 好黃 ！"},{"pid":"e8c2bb6ee794d4198ed7e757d846f82c69723324","tid":2425430,"uid":69083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"R.I.P.<br />\n祝達叔 來世再做中蟈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1bcb3a304ad431395c62ca41c369b42f655df","tid":2425430,"uid":47659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"話口賤個班<br />\n根本就係好好食就會去藍店個D人黎<br />\n仲有 一定會多謝支共開自遊行 賣東江水 賣疫苗<br />\n永遠都係自己欠人地 人地貢獻自己 廢老理論"},{"pid":"6b532a69f0ef9fa33a3d32fbbca42b7352229118","tid":2425430,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都係為錢拍戲<br />\n為錢衝去擁護極權<br />\n<br />\n飲水思源都唔識 只係錢銀關係<br />\n集體回憶都係用錢造出黎<br />\n吳孟達從來都冇愛過香港<br />\n係班傻仔響度過分浪漫化<br />\n<br />\n香港人冇欠佢 <br />\n冇良知嘅藍屍就係抵死"},{"pid":"64ecac35bee7ec10af995cd98cdae0325a47c57d","tid":2425430,"uid":2719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"TVB都係我童年回憶，真係由細睇到大電視撈飯，主題曲我唱到琅琅上口，到佢關台收皮，係咪要講好可惜？"},{"pid":"1f0fa408711194790cccf8b11a83e118109f733b","tid":2425430,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b532a69f0ef9fa33a3d32fbbca42b7352229118","tid":2425430,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都係為錢拍戲<br />\n為錢衝去擁護極權<br />\n<br />\n飲水思源都唔識 只係錢銀關係<br />\n集體回憶都係用錢造出黎<br />\n吳孟達從來都冇愛過香港<br />\n係班傻仔響度過分浪漫化<br />\n<br />\n香港人冇欠佢 <br />\n冇良知嘅藍屍就係抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"你笑藍屍死咪會變成同藍屍一樣咁惡毒囉，會失民意架⋯ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932f2f675dd79a6d3115c7ade0d743bf4dc9300a","tid":2425430,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：日日食m記用牛牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb9eee098adbef68f46f5bbbe78a392bd31fc65","tid":2425430,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"感謝 達哥咁多年帶俾大家歡笑<br />\n<br />\n利申 我搭黨鐵 用八達通<br />\n食M記<br />\n<br />\n但好黃"},{"pid":"09cb33266245e7e41d7f4db85e084b3fb051dbdf","tid":2425430,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6b532a69f0ef9fa33a3d32fbbca42b7352229118","tid":2425430,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都係為錢拍戲<br />\n為錢衝去擁護極權<br />\n<br />\n飲水思源都唔識 只係錢銀關係<br />\n集體回憶都係用錢造出黎<br />\n吳孟達從來都冇愛過香港<br />\n係班傻仔響度過分浪漫化<br />\n<br />\n香港人冇欠佢 <br />\n冇良知嘅藍屍就係抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"其實都同意<br />\n不過條友始終係一個成功演員嚟<br />\n係啲人心目中都有一定地位，呢啲唔關黃藍事。<br />\n有好多嘢意見唔同啫，但人地死左比一份尊重都唔得？"},{"pid":"887743aa02f7b77d6d7060965e7d91751dec72b0","tid":2425430,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"對電影業有貢獻，共同回憶大灑架? 有免死金牌架? 奶完共之後咪都係死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果成蟲 陳小春 pakho嗰堆死左，我一樣會拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc00a48c0342a1ad4d224e385ed18bd3dcf7afea","tid":2425430,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"我無特別感覺 唔認為要特別可惜 或者特別去眨低佢<br />\n<br />\n反而有批藍屍五毛借連登個名黎放負踩港 咁講唔過去 所以都係決定留言屌多次佢地老母<br />\n<br />\n今朝果條借達叔踩港既仆街一早扑左<br />\n<br />\n跟據佢既支那邏輯 689都係人黎 我地要尊重同珍惜佢 因為隻狗曾經登報屌八九六四<br />\n<br />\n傻既都知講唔通啦 借題發揮 轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n踩港矮化香港人先係呢班仆街既目的"},{"pid":"f348f0983addb2b1b567ebf6f5fd77778f4e91a3","tid":2425430,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"88052759f78747157d2728271ccb442dcec4a89f","tid":2425430,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGEK7Ht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGEK7Ht.jpg&h=7d763393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3752756b46bbe8ee6e7d103fc69c70a35a8d2f0e","tid":2425430,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"愛支病就係敵人<br />\n唔撚好同我講有咩貢獻<br />\n14億支那雞仲有貢獻過你"},{"pid":"acdebcef701e5cf19c9079cf37b06959afb96c61","tid":2425430,"uid":391618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔係想鬥黃<br />\n但<br />\n仲用淘寶,支那寶, 買中概股嘅人到底咩心態?<br />\n市場又唔係無 alternative 產品, 為一個幾毫去真金白銀支持中共同藍絲廢老有咩分別? <span class=\"red\">一邊口講反共一邊親手扶植惡魔, 再抱怨點解中共可以越來越惡, 根本係自食其果.</span><br />\n2019年之後可以避免都唔會用/買中國產品. 生活成本整體上升5-10%, 雖然支出會大咗, 但錢無咗可以再揾, <span class=\"red\">起碼我用外國貨可以心安理得, 大大聲屌柒你班仲用緊中國貨嘅柒頭.</span><br />\n通常呢個時候又會有人衝出黎話 &quot;咁你又用東江水?&quot;, 但如果有其他選擇我都唔會用. 東江水係市場壟斷性產品, 用一個壟斷者嘅身分去笑鳩人點解仲要繼續用同獨裁政權有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 我信仲有好多香港人同我一樣仲堅持緊. 請樓主唔好一竹篙屌鳩全香港人"},{"pid":"47f1035f2b65d3ad49d33a565b0c74f0787267c2","tid":2425430,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"你都幾難生活"},{"pid":"726c126537f4ee9ca77bc423bddc42b950bb532c","tid":2425430,"uid":297156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"快走啦。 <br />\n<br />\n支那岩你住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7f58b6233b1c810ccd271c7299f784e7c568e5","tid":2425430,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"true 垃圾"},{"pid":"88ee33e7651a924d3344891c164d3dcbafc14cff","tid":2425430,"uid":117584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"88052759f78747157d2728271ccb442dcec4a89f","tid":2425430,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGEK7Ht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGEK7Ht.jpg&h=7d763393&s={SIZE}\" />"}}